  "body": "### Overview\r\nRun an application that uses brownie in k8s using a security context\r\n```yaml\r\nsecurityContext:\r\n  allowPrivilegeEscalation: false\r\n  runAsUser: 10001\r\n  runAsGroup: 10001\r\n  capabilities:\r\n    drop: [\"ALL\"]\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Specification\r\n```yaml\r\nsecurityContext:\r\n  allowPrivilegeEscalation: false\r\n  runAsUser: 10001\r\n  runAsGroup: 10001\r\n  capabilities:\r\n    drop: [\"ALL\"]\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Result\r\n![image](https://github.com/eth-brownie/brownie/assets/111905706/d997da97-8de4-4ad2-bb0f-eaf0d5e5d15c)\r\n\r\nBrownie only executes with the root user\r\n![image](https://github.com/eth-brownie/brownie/assets/111905706/28aa3502-4b86-4507-b2cd-11431ef00a73)\r\n\r\nseems `cache.db` and `topics.json` are created during the Brownie initialization.\r\n",
